import "./form.css";
function Form() {
  return (
    <form>
      <container>
        <input type="checkbox" />
        <label>I read</label>
      </container>
      <container>
        <input type="checkbox" />
        <label>I accept</label>
      </container>
      <container>
        <input type="checkbox" checked />
        <label>I want1</label>
      </container>
      <container>
        <input type="checkbox" checked />
        <label>I want2</label>
      </container>
    </form>
  );
}

export default Form;
